@startuml task-lifecycle
' AgentTask state machine.
' Source of truth: docs/src/controller/task-lifecycle.md
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam nodesep 30
skinparam ranksep 45
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #E6E6FA
  BorderColor #4A148C
  FontColor #2a0a4a
  ArrowColor #4A148C
}
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC
skinparam NoteBorderColor #8B7500
skinparam NoteFontSize 11
hide empty description

state "Pending" as Pending
state "Provisioning" as Provisioning
state "Running" as Running
state "Completing" as Completing
state "Succeeded" as Succeeded
state "Failed" as Failed
state "TimedOut" as TimedOut
state "Terminating" as Terminating
state "any state" as AnyState #F5F5F5

note right of Pending : initial
note right of Provisioning : creating Pod/PVC
note right of Completing : collecting artifacts,\nscheduling teardown

' ---- Main path ----
[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Provisioning : references validated
Provisioning --> Running : Pod Ready
Running --> Completing : completion signal\nOR timeout OR exit
Completing --> Succeeded : success reported
Completing --> Failed : failure reported
Completing --> TimedOut : timeout hit

' ---- Failure and retry paths ----
Pending -[#0D47A1]-> Failed : spec irreconcilable:\nPersistenceNotAllowed /\nClassConstraintViolation
Provisioning -[#0D47A1]-> Failed : unrecoverable Pod-start error;\nretryable under backoffLimit
Running -[#0D47A1]-> Failed : involuntary Pod disruption mid-run;\nretryable under backoffLimit
Failed -[#0D47A1]-> Provisioning : backoffLimit retry:\nstatus.retries < backoffLimit

' ---- Teardown ----
AnyState --> Terminating : on delete or after TTL

' ---- Layout hints ----
Succeeded -[hidden]-> AnyState
TimedOut -[hidden]-> AnyState
@enduml
